How to do Key Word Research:
------------------------------
1. copy the product name like below from CPA market offer that you want to work
	- CBD Oil
	- League of Legends

2. paste in search box
	- Niche Laboratory (https://digitalmarketingsupermarket.com/tool/niche-laboratory/)
	- www.keyword.io (https://www.keyword.io/)

3. click on search button

4. wait few minute
6. copy the keywords and paste in text/node pad file
7. copy the keywords and paste from text/node pad file to excel file
8. if keywords has commas, you can separate it through https://www.dcode.fr/values-separation
9. to find dublicate use (=countif(A:A,A1)>1) function:
	- select all keywords of excel
	- go to Format menu --> conditional formating
	- Format rules --> Custom format is
	- in "Custom format is" text box, paste =countif(A:A,A1)>1 and select color, click on done button

10. delete dublicate keywords
11. select all from excel --> Data menu --> short (A-Z)
12. now, remove informational keywords and irrelevent keywords (who, which, what, how related keywords and other irrelevent keywords)
     by (x) mark in excel and delete all

13. copy each of the keywords (one by one) --> go to google trand (country: United State, 90 days) --> search, download, make average
      and write (value) in excel another field at the side of keyword  (keyword | average value)

14. select all values and --> Data menu --> short (Z-A)

15. copy first 25 keywords for your advertizing


